OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early brightness for
OL,6,FAyrshire and Lanarkshire, otherwise a
OL,7,Fmostly cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain, occasionally heavy especially
OL,9,Facross Argyll. The rain turns more
OL,10,Fshowery in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy during
OL,13,Fthe evening and through the night with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of heavy and perhaps
OL,15,Fthundery rain. Clearer, drier spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping in the west towards morning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FCloudier at first with heavy,
OL,19,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing.
OL,20,FThen bright or sunny spells and
OL,21,Fscattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
